<h1 class="doc-page-title">Staff Role Returns</h1>
<p class="doc-page-lead">Annual staff role return system for GDD (Government Digital and Data) role reporting with skills tracking.</p>

<p>Documentation for staff role returns is being developed. This will cover:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Submitting annual role returns</li>
    <li>GDD role selection</li>
    <li>Secondary skills tracking</li>
    <li>Reporting period logic (Apr-Mar, due 31 Mar)</li>
    <li>Overdue return tracking</li>
    <li>GDD roles and skills management</li>
</ul>

<div class="alert alert-info mt-4">
    <p class="mb-0">For user stories and detailed feature information, see <a href="@Url.Action("UserStories", "Documentation")">User stories</a>.</p>
</div>

